description.en_us: A backup / restore plugin, with multiple backup slot

introduction.en_us:
A backup / restore plugin, with multiple backup slot

Features:

- Comment for backup
- Extra backup for removed world
- Time protection for slot
- Backup size display
introduction.zh_cn:
多槽位备份/回档插件

一些特性：

- 带注释的备份
- 对被删除世界的额外备份
- 插槽时间保护
- 备份大小显示
